# ShortLink

A simple URL shortener built with React and local storage.

## Features

* Shorten URLs with custom aliases
* Track clicks and referrers
* View detailed analytics

## Demo

[https://shortlink.pages.dev](https://shortlink.pages.dev)

## Development

1. Clone the repository
2. Run `npm install`
3. Run `npm start`
4. Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) in your browser

## Deployment

1. Run `npm run build`
2. Upload the `build` folder to your hosting provider

